=Description=

"In this interview, Brent Hoberman, Partner at PROfounders Capital and co-founder of Lastminute.com, offers some insight into the types of businesses investors are looking at in the Collaborative Consumption sector.

He also outlines some of the most significant changes to online business models since he started Lastminute.com, including the influence of web giants such as Google and Facebook.

The interview was filmed at the March 2012 Collaborative Consumption summit at Nesta, which focused on new business models in the sector."

